+## Target System Direction
+
+Scout evolves from an evidence-first research engine into a self-improving problem-solving agent platform.
+
+```mermaid
+flowchart TD
+  UI[Streaming Chat UI<br/>partial answers + trace/debug panels]
+  Planner[Intent Planner<br/>deterministic overrides + LLM fallback<br/>typed task DAG]
+  Executor[Agent Executor Controller<br/>budgets + permissions]
+  Researcher[Researcher xN]
+  Crawler[Crawler]
+  Evidence[Evidence + Verify]
+  Answer[Answer + Critic]
+  Retrieval[Hybrid Retrieval → Reranker<br/>BM25 + vector recall + cross-encoder rerank]
+  Memory[Tiered Memory + Curator<br/>working + episodic + semantic + procedural]
+  Stores[Stores<br/>Postgres + Qdrant + Redis/BullMQ]
+  Harness[Harness + Evals + Self-learning Loop<br/>traces → learned routing/source strategies → procedural memory]
+  Cache[Cross-cutting Cache<br/>prompt/LLM + retrieval/rerank + embedding + answer TTL]
+
+  UI --> Planner --> Executor
+  Executor --> Researcher
+  Executor --> Crawler
+  Executor --> Evidence
+  Executor --> Answer
+  Executor --> Retrieval --> Memory --> Stores --> Harness
+  Harness -. improves .-> Planner
+  Cache -. supports .-> Executor
+  Cache -. supports .-> Retrieval
+  Cache -. invalidated by .-> Memory
+```
+
+The current implementation starts with **M0: measurement foundation**. Every later capability must move an eval number without regressing existing gates.
+
+```bash
+npm run eval:m0
+npm run eval:ci
+npm run eval:phase2
+npm run eval:phase3
+```
+
+See `docs/SCOUT_PLATFORM_PLAN.md` for the full milestone plan.
+
